'''Galaxy News Service''' was a media company and one of the original signatory sponsors of the [[Corporate Sector Authority/Legends|Corporate Sector Authority]]. It was second only to [[Imperial HoloVision]] in popularity among readers. Galaxy's major shareholder was [[Millennium Entertainments]].<ref name="HSCS" />

